00:02:50.760 --> 00:02:55.720
For the full break down of what sold, for
how much, and what it cost to make, check

00:02:55.720 --> 00:02:58.960
this guide on my website at tarouwowguides.com

00:02:58.960 --> 00:03:06.920
4,346.64g in profit isn't bad but when you
see it took over 31k gold it'll make you rethink

00:03:06.920 --> 00:03:11.500
if the risk is worth it or not. Elixirs are
good for players without a lot of gold to

00:03:11.500 --> 00:03:19.720
sink into Flasks. Just be careful as you saw
some didn't net a profit at all and were a

00:03:19.720 --> 00:03:26.470
waste of time as well as some Flasks were
too. To make sure you don't make these mistakes.

00:03:26.470 --> 00:03:31.620
Try getting mats for the same price or cheaper
than you can sell the item for and don't count

00:03:31.620 --> 00:03:35.070
procs. That way you should always net a profit.

00:03:35.070 --> 00:03:39.650
Finally, Elixir spec so far in Cataclysm is
harder to have success with than it was in

00:03:39.650 --> 00:03:44.780
Wrath so tread lightly and be careful you
aren't wasting your time and losing gold.

